               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit “Psalter” (fols. 1r-201ra)
 I-1) Mazmura Dāwit “Psalms of
                     David” (fols. 1r-155v) 
 I-2) Maḥālǝya nabiyāt “The Canticles of the
                     Prophets” (fols. 156r-173r) 
 I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy “Song of Songs” (fols.
                     173r-181v)
 I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols. 182ra-196vb)
                     I-5) ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (fols. 196vb-202ra)
 I-6) Mazmura
                     dǝngǝl “Psalter of the Virgin” (strophes distributed between sections of Texts
                     I-1, I-2, I-3, fols. 1r-181v)
 
 Additiones 1-5.</summary>
