                        <seg type="rubrication">Name of St Mary in Texts I-4, I-5 and I-6; name of
                           Jesus Christ in Text I-4; name of Archangel Gabriel in Text I-5; initial
                           line of the inscription on fol. 1r; title of Texts I-2, I-3, I-5; three
                           groups of two adjacent lines on the incipit page of Text I-4; title and
                           number of the Pss. and Canticles; number of the Songs; initial line of
                           the Pss. of Text I-6; title and part of the incipit of the daily readings
                           of Text I-4; doxology following each Song; refrains of Texts I-4 and I-5
                           (written out fully or abbreviated); name and traditional interpretation
                           of the Hebrew letters in Ps. 118; a few single words in Texts I-4 and
                           I-5; elements of the punctuation signs and text dividers; Ethiopic
                           numerals or their elements.</seg>
                     </handNote>
